655
00:51:27,480 --> 00:51:29,480
[SPEAKER_01] Fama se stvorila oko svega.

656
00:51:29,480 --> 00:51:30,480
[SPEAKER_01] Laktoza, ono.

657
00:51:30,480 --> 00:51:42,480
